        dc:description           "Figure 6. (A, B) Filaguria lithocrustata sp. nov., SAM A27523: (A) ovicelled autozooid, X70; (B) autozooids and a small kenozooid, X40. (C–E) Sclerodomus myriozoides, SAM A27530: (C) part of colony plus young branch, X15; (D) abfrontal view of colony showing four series of autozoids, X30; (E) aperture showing associated avicularia." ;
